org.GameLogic.Board

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.GameLogic.Board.Map

  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    Data structure storing all tiles on given coordinates. Uses a HashBasedTable provided by Guava.

    • Field Detail

      • EXPECTED

        public static final int EXPECTED
        To minimize the effect of the Hashtable updating its inner data structure, we just expect the tiles to stay in the range between -128 to 127 in x and y coordinates. This means that the Hashtable will update itself(resize) when one side(left,right,down,up) surpasses 128 tiles. We can save 2^16 tiles without resizing the map in the best case.

        Constant Field Values
